title: Eddie Has 'Money Talk' With His Kids + Maren Morris And Ryan Hurd On Life As New Parents + Food Feud: McDonald’s vs Chick-Fil-A
itunes:title: Eddie Has 'Money Talk' With His Kids + Maren Morris And Ryan Hurd On Life As New Parents + Food Feud: McDonald’s vs Chick-Fil-A
description:
Eddie had to have a talk with his kids on how to spend their money. We debated whether or not he was out of line. Maren Morris and her husband Ryan Hurd stop by the studio to talk about what life is like as new parents during the coronavirus. Plus, we put two famous french fries against each other in this week’s FOOD FEUD!
